title: September 11 - The New Pearl Harbor (x264-vorbis-namedchapters)
description:
September 11 - The New Pearl Harbor, by Massimo Mazzucco (2013)

Including a full named chapters index as provided in the original DVDs.
Chapter index #4 of DVD 3 ("Fuel in elevators shafts" theory) has been
preserved (the index is missing in the DVD menu). The chapter starts a
few seconds before the actual info screen.

This is certainly one of the most powerful 9/11 documentaries out there.
Although it begins with questions that might appear a bit vague at
first, the narrative eventually gets more & more cogent, especially in
the second half which describes the physical evidence regarding the
collapse of the Twin Towers as well as Building 7, much of which is
based on the research of Architects & Engineers for 9/11 Truth, therefor
i'd recommend to watch the whole thing before drawing any conclusions.
